    "Gene ontology.",
    "We assess the ability of learned representations to predict protein function using a Gene Ontology dataset originally published in the PROBE set of benchmark tasks 8.",
    "The dataset relies on experimental annotations from UniProtKB and/or SwissProt and UniProtGOA and considers gene ontology groups from all three groups of annotations: that is, molecular function, cellular compartment and biological process.",
